533,0.02299308,-0.01132992,0.04875744,-0.04146542,-0.00538492,0.03665552,0.06565021,-0.00274818,0.03427209,0.01745538,-0.01742160,0.01411710,0.06760319,0.01082835,0.04138670,0.02916749,0.00194135,-0.05939592,0.03387938,-0.01552276,0.06268393,0.00832384,-0.00950369,0.01544040,-0.07137377,-0.03191070,0.03994561,-0.01550527,-0.08313023,0.06126572,-0.00769400,-0.00936822,0.01490393,0.05156722,0.02421931,-0.01299947,-0.04048916,0.00435579,-0.01364309,0.06919670,0.01398973,-0.03225946]',E'Build and install the ANTLR4 runtime\n\nMany Linux distributions do not currently ship a new enough ANTLR4 C++ runtime, so\nif yours doesn''t, build it from source before configuring CMake.\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/mysql-src\ncd ~/mysql-src\ngit clone --depth 1 --branch 4.13.1 --sparse \\\n  https://github.com/antlr/antlr4.git antlr4-runtime\ncd antlr4-runtime\ngit sparse-checkout set runtime/Cpp\nmkdir -p build\ncd build\nscl enable gcc-toolset-14 -- cmake ../runtime/Cpp \\\n  -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DANTLR_BUILD_CPP_TESTS=OFF\nscl enable gcc-toolset-14 -- cmake --build . --parallel $(nproc --all)\nmake install DESTDIR=~/mysql-src\n```','{"source": "mysql", "version": "9.0", "language": "sql", "title": "Build Instructions for MySQL Shell", "section_title": "INSTALL", "url": "https://github.com/mysql/mysql-shell/blob/master/INSTALL.md", "topics": "mysql/shell,INSTALL", "categories": "database,sql,relational,shell,cli"}');
