2299078,0.00819889,-0.02243283,0.05480095,-0.01538750,-0.00177185,0.00010887,0.11016192,0.05553771,-0.01888663,0.07794230,-0.03029525,-0.02360825,0.04820256,-0.02012029,0.08071985,0.06115802,0.01923129,-0.06153273,0.00694875,0.02411839,0.04558561,0.06147470,-0.05669271,0.03966481,-0.05335578,0.04004938,-0.02498403,-0.02292817,0.00690179,0.04330340,0.02565833,-0.03098264,0.01192527,0.10002833,-0.03959695,-0.00545693,0.02301504,0.02832836,-0.04962800,0.09770706,0.00836120,-0.01370706]',E'Windows\n\n1. Create the build directory:\n```bash\nmkdir bld\ncd bld\n```\n2. Configure with Visual Studio:\n```bash\ncmake .. -G "Visual Studio 16" \\\n    -DMYSQL_SOURCE_DIR=../../mysql-server \\\n    -DMYSQL_BUILD_DIR=../../mysql-server/bld \\\n    -DBUNDLED_ANTLR_DIR=../../antlr4-runtime/build \\\n    -DHAVE_PYTHON=1 \\\n    -DPYTHON_LIBRARY=<path_to_python_library> \\\n    -DPYTHON_INCLUDE_DIR=<python_src>/include\n```\n3. Open `mysh.sln` in Visual Studio 2019 and build the desired configuration.\n\nAll Windows dependencies must be compiled with matching settings (Release vs.\nDebug and /MD vs. /MT).','{"source": "mysql", "version": "9.0", "language": "sql", "title": "Build Instructions for MySQL Shell", "section_title": "INSTALL", "url": "https://github.com/mysql/mysql-shell/blob/master/INSTALL.md", "topics": "mysql/shell,INSTALL", "categories": "database,sql,relational,shell,cli"}');
